bug.short_desc: [sec] JNI bridge for Windows Data Protection services

long_desc.thetext: Created attachment 86319 DLL source project and compiled release and debug versions

Created attachment 86501 The zip of new Java fragment for Windows
This is the fragment encapsuling Windows DLL. The fragment provides DTAPI-backed secure storage via org.eclipse.equinox.security.auth.secureStorage extension point.

Created attachment 86729 Updated fragment
The fragment updated with changes to interfaces and functionality of the main account storage module.
The new fragment added to the incubator under equinox-incubator/security/org.eclipse.equinox.security.auth.win32.x86.
